  3.700388907022374*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"19f373b3-2582-4c2d-ad1b-\
598d415dcf80"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "We set the directory. This cell is not an initializ",
 StyleBox["ation cell, and is not saved in the .m file. Inde",
  FontWeight->"Regular"],
 "ed this is only needed if we run ",
 StyleBox["PRIMAT-main.nb",
  FontFamily->"Source Code Pro",
  FontWeight->"Regular"],
 " directly.\nOtherwise if we load it as a package (loading ",
 StyleBox["PRIMAT-main.m",
  FontFamily->"Source Code Pro",
  FontWeight->"Regular"],
 " file), then we need to determine the absolute path and this is stored in \
$PackageDirectory."
}], "Text",
