  "d36a837e-212e-4a4c-bb27-ab6884589f5e"],
 " is the weak magnetism constant.  See [Horowitz&Li] for definition with the \
value given by its Table 1. \nNote that all expressions in [Seckel 1993] seem \
to have a factor 2 difference. That is all interaction rates involving the \
weak magnetism in [Seckel 1993] are underestimated by a factor 2. Expressions \
in [Lopez et al. 1997] seem correct however."
}], "Text",
