Cell[TextData[{
 "We can also reduce the network to its 12 first reactions. This is enough \
for the first light elements. \nIt consists in the first 12 reactions of the \
tabulated reactions (those in the file ",
 StyleBox["TabulatedReactionsFile",
  FontFamily->"Source Code Pro",
  FontSize->13,
  FontWeight->"SemiBold"],
 ").\nFurthermore, if ",
 StyleBox["$ReducedNetwork",
  FontFamily->"Source Code Pro",
  FontSize->13,
  FontWeight->"SemiBold"],
 " is selected, no extra analytic reactions are added so that we really have \
only a total of 12+1 reactions (because we also have weak interactions)."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.937272216448125*^9},ExpressionUUID->"88be4a4e-d418-4ae1-849c-\
3293e56f8f86"],

