   RowBox[{"$PENRatesIntegralsPoints", "=", "200"}], ";"}], 
  RowBox[{"(*", 
   RowBox[{"200", " ", "is", " ", "enough"}], " ", "*)"}]}]], "Input",
 InitializationCell->True,
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.936295303406478*^9, 3.9362953035241213`*^9}},
