Cell["\<\
A function to load a precompiled function, or to store it if it was not \
computed and stored previously .
If $Recompile=True, then the compilation of the function is performed even if \
there is a version stored and it tries to delete the previous library.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.936244160552355*^9, 3.936244223700227*^9}, {
  3.937274857879829*^9, 
  3.937274863134316*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"163dc80e-6ac0-4b39-9334-\
