Cell["\<\
The most accurate estimation of Neff, given the options chosen, is (because \
it uses directly the results of NEVO, and note that it requires \
NeutrinosGenerations=3 or whatever has been used in NEVO.):\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9351136378821287`*^9, 
  3.935113683452149*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"536911bd-f9e1-43bb-8909-\
fdd11175f0d7"],

