Cell["\<\
Shift in the weak rates due to spectral distortions of neutrino distribution \
functions.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7828143940794353`*^9, 
  3.78281441344271*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"6ef6f2fc-a095-4fbf-a419-\
