cf538e9b058a"],

Cell["\<\
We plot the amplitude of the finite mass corrections. This is essentially \
similar to Fig 8.1 of [Kernan] but the result is a little different since \
here we have put all the finite nucleon mass effects, and [Kernan] did not.\
\>", "Text",
 InitializationCell->True,
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.698399594991313*^9, 3.698399610177526*^9}, 
   3.6984904026730337`*^9, {3.698490824431851*^9, 3.698490843701408*^9}, {
