Cell["\<\
We define dictionaries to handle species. We associate a number to each species
It is a simple correspondance between names and position of the species in \
the list, or between the names and the pair (neutron,proton).\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.715950634620714*^9, 
  3.715950722130125*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"951c0f1a-387a-47c6-a099-\
