Cell["Lists of analytic reactions (86 reactions)", "Subsection",ExpressionUUID->"d7449b44-d834-4d0f-b16b-78faf81b2d28"],

Cell["\<\
We have a list of 86 reactions for which we use analytic fits from the \
literature
In principle these reactions could be tabulated and incorporated into the \
external file but we prefer to keep their analytic forms.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"8442e83a-37fa-4319-a10e-58965764b0ee"],

