Cell["\<\
LoadRates is the function which does all that. Let us call it. It will stop \
and quit if one of the reactions is inconsistent (not conservation of N nor \
Z).\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"deaa1b68-c131-46b7-b2f8-69ab0ff8ca21"],

