Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Numerical abundance functions", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.715950854899377*^9, 
  3.715950861772547*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"cfa03aeb-fbb1-41b1-962b-\
356cb60be842"],

Cell["\<\
We also need the list of functions to store the results of the numerical \
integrations. 
We have divided our BBN period in 3 eras. 

High temperature (HT), 
Middle temperature (MT)
Low temperature (LT).

So for instance the abundance of a species, say Lithium7 whose shortname is \
\[OpenCurlyQuote]Li7\[CloseCurlyQuote], during  the HT period at a given \
cosmological time t, is

YHT[\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Li7\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]][t]. 

Eventually we are interested in the values YLT[\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]species\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]][tend] where tend is the final time of our numerical \
integration.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.715950236241974*^9, 3.7159502425850277`*^9}, {
  3.7159505685891247`*^9, 3.715950626211178*^9}, {3.722699365263047*^9, 
  3.722699406345842*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b842af13-af48-4912-a21e-\
17dc48e333e1"],

Cell[BoxData[{
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"KeyQ", "[", "key_", "]"}], ":=", 
    RowBox[{"MemberQ", "[", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"NamesWithWeightsAll", "[", 
       RowBox[{"[", 
        RowBox[{"All", ",", "1"}], "]"}], "]"}], ",", "key"}], "]"}]}], ";"}],
   "\[IndentingNewLine]"}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"YHT", "[", 
     RowBox[{"key_", "?", "KeyQ"}], "]"}], "[", "t_", "]"}], ":=", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"Y", "[", "\"\<HT\>\"", "]"}], "[", "key", "]"}], "[", "t", 
    "]"}]}], ";"}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"YMT", "[", 
     RowBox[{"key_", "?", "KeyQ"}], "]"}], "[", "t_", "]"}], ":=", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"Y", "[", "\"\<MT\>\"", "]"}], "[", "key", "]"}], "[", "t", 
    "]"}]}], ";"}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"YLT", "[", 
     RowBox[{"key_", "?", "KeyQ"}], "]"}], "[", "t_", "]"}], ":=", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"Y", "[", "\"\<LT\>\"", "]"}], "[", "key", "]"}], "[", "t", 
    "]"}]}], ";"}]}], "Input",
