Cell["\<\
Now we can build the rhs of the differential equation. This is obtained from \
its formal expression \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]FormalReactions\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] in which time dependence is added thanks to some \
replacement rules.\
\>", "Text",
 InitializationCell->True,
