Cell["\<\
The end values for neutrons and protons at high temperatures are used as \
initial conditions for the middle temperature era. 
We use thermostatistical equilibrium for the species defined in the list \
ListThermalValuesMT below, and 0 otherwise.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.715955050294293*^9, 3.7159550647780447`*^9}, {
  3.7159550978736973`*^9, 3.715955099942622*^9}, {3.71750575193504*^9, 
